{
  "id": "class_0063",
  "name": "Scorched Royal Herald",
  "title_completion": "a Scorched Royal Herald",
  "flavor_text": "The Mad King's decrees don't merely command \u2014 they burn. You carry his edicts etched in living flame, each proclamation a brand pressed into the air itself, sealing the throne room in a haze of ash and obedience. No one questions the sovereign seal when it's written in fire.",
